-------------<br>
<br>
2.8 million in additional revenue for little or no cost (if you believe there will be any better support on Stormhammer I have some swampland to sell you) is far from shortsighted. Just not particularly kind to the players.<br>
<br>
Fact is that this will have very little affect on FV. The kind of people that play on FV aren't interested in this type of thing. It's either roleplayers or powergamers who wanted a fresh server and a challenge--not particularly groups likely to do this.<br>
